cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper deals with computer vision algorithms for optic disc and cup segmentation, which is a common problem in medical image analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves optimization of the neural network, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with medical image analysis, which can be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
